{
  "stem": "13690.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he gave us a place, again now, to go in a house where mother was there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now what arrangements were made afterwards to try to save yourself?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then this was already going in towards the end of 1942, going into beginning of 1943 where we found out that this Radomsko ghetto, that this famous ghetto, was completely-- 10,000 Jews were sent off to Treblinka, to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time was no way already to go anyplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father, luckily, secured through negotiation-- probably for a long time with a good friend of my father, which he knew and had befriended himself many years before-- and he built a bunker in the town.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he was quite a hand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, he was an architect from profession, himself, and he was an intelligent man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He risked his life and his family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I want, at this point, just to bring out one more point-- the hardship about the Poles upon the Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not a question of collaboration, of helping.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only country in Europe, where that sentence for helping or hiding a Jew, was Poland, and Poland only.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Jew in Holland or in France for helping a Jew were not severely punished the way they were punished in Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of the person who built this bunker for us was Yusef and Maria Placzek, P-L-A-C-Z-E-K.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He built two bunkers-- as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The one, just to be able to sustain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two, another one in case of, really, danger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would describe the first one where most of the time we spent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was on the attic whereby the-- on the attic, we could sleep there.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
